nd exhilarating new maps with breathtaking views. Ascend grand peaks, navigate vast caves, climb skyscrapers, and discover hidden shortcuts as you find your path to the top. Compete with friends and conquer leaderboards in asynchronous multiplayer modes. From exploring mountain environments to scaling urban settings, feel the rush of climbing without ropes, and experience breathtaking vistas as you scale new heights.", "short_description": "The Climb 2 brings the thrill of climbing alive with a new city setting, exciting new maps, new events, and more. Ascend epic peaks, navigate vast caves, scale skyscrapers, and discover shortcuts as you find your path to the top. Compete with friends in multiplayer and conquer leaderboards."}]}, "developer_name": "Crytek", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "http://www.theclimbgame.com/privacy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "http://www.theclimbgame.com/terms", "publisher_name": "Crytek", "support_website_url": "https://theclimbgame.kayako.com/", "website_url": "http://www.theclimbgame.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_SOME", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": null, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["ARCADE", "EXPLORATION", "SPORTS"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["es_VE", "de", "es_AR", "ko", "es_PE", "en", "fr", "es_PR", "ja", "es_CL", "es_MX", "es_CO"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "1032523570808901"}, "review_messages": [""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974593_471778593997125_7874371937809642624_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=i2slgZNULzQQ7kNvgG5iK1H&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAbf7Ybu55AsHCS7QwERsoWFWRDyAu-ULcWl8FTCBMG4g&oe=66D9A598"}, "is_concept": false, "is_test": false, "is_trial_offer_valid": false, "display_name": "The Climb 2", "platform": "ANDROID_6DOF", "context_category": {"context_category": "GAMES", "id": "2743326035925534"}, "context_topics": [{"topic_name": "Sports", "id": "2776542286000603"}, {"topic_name": "Arcade", "id": "1592192974313489"}], "release_date": 1614880800, "lastRevision": {"nodes": [{"id": "3400583116649443", "release_type": "MANAGED", "administration_status": "APPROVED", "pdp_metadata": {"application": {"default_locale": "en_US", "id": "2617233878395214", "is_first_party": false, "enables_in_app_ads": false, "is_concept": false, "platform": "ANDROID_6DOF"}, "iarc_cert": {"id": "726730208107688"}, "iarc_email": null, "msrp": null, "translations": {"nodes": [{"images": {"nodes": []}, "id": "2726375777604360", "locale": "es_LA", "screenshots": [], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "The Climb 2", "keywords": ["Sports"], "long_description": "Vive la aventura de trepar con The Climb 2: explora una flamante ciudad e incre\u00edbles nuevos mapas con vistas alucinantes. Conquista cimas \u00e9picas, explora cuevas enormes, escala rascacielos y descubre atajos ocultos en tu camino a lo m\u00e1s alto. Compite con amigos y conquista los marcadores en los modos multijugador asincr\u00f3nicos. Explora tanto monta\u00f1as como ambientes urbanos, siente la emoci\u00f3n de escalar sin cuerdas y disfruta de vistas \u00e9picas desde las alturas.", "short_description": "The Climb 2 te acerca la aventura de trepar en un nuevo entorno urbano, flamantes mapas fant\u00e1sticos, novedosos eventos y mucho m\u00e1s. Conquista cimas \u00e9picas, explora cuevas enormes, escala rascacielos y descubre atajos en tu camino a lo m\u00e1s alto. Compite con amigos en el modo multijugador y conquista los marcadores."}, {"images": {"nodes": []}, "id": "1199242620444180", "locale": "de_DE", "screenshots": [], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "The Climb 2", "keywords": ["Sports"], "long_description": "Mit The Climb 2 wird der Nervenkitzel des Kletterns zum Leben erweckt \u2013 erkunde das neue Stadt-Setting und die aufregenden neuen Karten mit fantastischen Aussichten. Erklimme epische Gipfel, navigiere durch riesige H\u00f6hlen, klettere an Wolkenkratzern hoch und entdecke auf dem Weg nach oben geheime Abk\u00fcrzungen. Miss dich im asynchronen Mehrspieler-Modus mit Freunden und erobere die Bestenlisten. Von der Erkundung von Gebirgslandschaften bis hin zu st\u00e4dtischen Umgebungen \u2013 erlebe den Rausch des Kletterns ohne Seile und genie\u00dfe atemberaubende Aussichten, w\u00e4hrend du immer h\u00f6her klimmst.", "short_description": "The Climb 2 erweckt den Nervenkitzel des Kletterns mit einem neuen Stadt-Setting, aufregenden neuen Karten, neuen Events und mehr zum Leben. Erklimme epische Gipfel, navigiere durch riesige H\u00f6hlen, klettere an Wolkenkratzern hoch und entdecke auf dem Weg nach oben hilfreiche Abk\u00fcrzungen. Miss dich im Mehrspieler-Modus mit Freunden und erobere die Bestenlisten."}, {"images": {"nodes": []}, "id": "802756087126225", "locale": "ja_JP", "screenshots": [], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "The Climb 2", "keywords": ["Sports"], "long_description": "The Climb 2\u3067\u81e8\u5834\u611f\u3068\u30b9\u30ea\u30eb\u6e80\u70b9\u306e\u30af\u30e9\u30a4\u30df\u30f3\u30b0\u306b\u6311\u6226\u3002\u65b0\u305f\u306a\u821e\u53f0\u3068\u306a\u308b\u90fd\u5e02\u3084\u3001\u606f\u3092\u5451\u3080\u7d76\u666f\u306e\u523a\u6fc0\u7684\u306a\u65b0\u30de\u30c3\u30d7\u3092\u63a2\u7d22\u3057\u307e\u3057\u3087\u3046\u3002\u96c4\u5927\u306a\u5c71\u306e\u9802\u4e0a\u3092\u76ee\u6307\u3057\u305f\u308a\u3001\u5e83\u5927\u306a\u6d1e\u7a9f\u3092\u63a2\u7d22\u3057\u305f\u308a\u3001\u6469\u5929\u697c\u3092\u3088\u3058\u767b\u3063\u305f\u308a\u3057\u306a\u304c\u3089\u3001\u30b4\u30fc\u30eb\u306b\u5230\u9054\u3059\u308b\u8fd1\u9053\u3092\u63a2\u3057\u307e\u3057\u3087\u3046\u3002\u975e\u540c\u671f\u30de\u30eb\u30c1\u30d7\u30ec\u30a4\u30e2\u30fc\u30c9\u3067\u30d5\u30ec\u30f3\u30c9\u3068\u7af6\u4e89\u3057\u3001\u30e9\u30f3\u30ad\u30f3\u30b0\u5236\u8987\u3092\u76ee\u6307\u3059\u3053\u3068\u3082\u3067\u304d\u307e\u3059\u3002\u5c71\u5cb3\u5730\u5e2f\u3092\u63a2\u7d22\u3057\u305f\u308a\u90fd\u4f1a\u306e\u30d3\u30eb\u3092\u3088\u3058\u767b\u3063\u305f\u308a\u3001\u30ed\u30fc\u30d7\u306a\u3057\u306e\u30af\u30e9\u30a4\u30df\u30f3\u30b0\u306e\u9ad8\u63da\u611f\u3092\u5473\u308f\u3044\u3001\u65b0\u305f\u306a\u9ad8\u307f\u306b\u5230\u9054\u3057\u3066\u606f\u3092\u5451\u3080\u666f\u8272\u3092\u582a\u80fd\u3057\u3066\u304f\u3060\u3055\u3044\u3002", "short_description": "The Climb 2\u306f\u81e8\u5834\u611f\u3068\u30b9\u30ea\u30eb\u6e80\u70b9\u306e\u30af\u30e9\u30a4\u30df\u30f3\u30b0\u30b2\u30fc\u30e0\u3067\u3059\u3002\u65b0\u305f\u306a\u821e\u53f0\u3068\u306a\u308b\u90fd\u5e02\u3001\u30a8\u30ad\u30b5\u30a4\u30c6\u30a3\u30f3\u30b0\u306a\u65b0\u30de\u30c3\u30d7\u3001\u65b0\u4f5c\u30a4\u30d9\u30f3\u30c8\u306a\u3069\u304c\u76db\u308a\u3060\u304f\u3055\u3093\u3002\u4f1d\u8aac\u306e\u5c71\u306e\u9802\u4e0a\u3092\u76ee\u6307\u3057\u305f\u308a\u3001\u5e83\u5927\u306a\u6d1e\u7a9f\u3092\u63a2\u7d22\u3057\u305f\u308a\u3001\u6469\u5929\u697c\u3092\u3088\u3058\u767b\u3063\u305f\u308a\u3057\u306a\u304c\u3089\u3001\u30b4\u30fc\u30eb\u306b\u5230\u9054\u3059\u308b\u8fd1\u9053\u3092\u63a2\u3057\u307e\u3057\u3087\u3046\u3002\u30de\u30eb\u30c1\u30d7\u30ec\u30a4\u3067\u30d5\u30ec\u30f3\u30c9\u3068\u7af6\u4e89\u3057\u3001\u30e9\u30f3\u30ad\u30f3\u30b0\u5236\u8987\u3092\u76ee\u6307\u3057\u3066\u304f\u3060\u3055\u3044\u3002"}, {"images": {"nodes": []}, "id": "780171735861684", "locale": "ko_KR", "screenshots": [], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "The Climb 2", "keywords": ["Sports"], "long_description": "\uc0c8\ub85c\uc6b4 \ub3c4\uc2dc \ubc30\uacbd, \ud765\ubbf8\ub85c\uc6b4 \uc2e0\uaddc \ub9f5, \uc2e0\uaddc \uc774\ubca4\ud2b8 \ub4f1\uc73c\ub85c \uac00\ub4dd\ud55c The Climb 2\ub294 \ud074\ub77c\uc774\ubc0d\uc758 \uc9dc\ub9bf\ud568\uc744 \uadf8\ub300\ub85c \uc120\uc0ac\ud569\ub2c8\ub2e4. \uc0b0 \uc815\uc0c1\uae4c\uc9c0 \ub4f1\ubc18\ud558\uace0, \ub4dc\ub113\uc740 \ub3d9\uad74\uc744 \ud0d0\ud5d8\ud558\uace0, \uace0\uce35 \uac74\ubb3c\uc744 \uc624\ub974\uace0, \uc228\uaca8\uc9c4 \uc9c0\ub984\uae38\uc744 \ubc1c\uacac\ud574 \uaf2d\ub300\uae30\uc5d0 \ub3c4\ub2ec\ud558\uc138\uc694. \ube44\ub3d9\uae30\uc2dd \uba40\ud2f0\ud50c\ub808\uc774 \ubaa8\ub4dc\ub85c \uce5c\uad6c\uc640 \uacbd\uc7c1\ud574 \ub9ac\ub354\ubcf4\ub4dc\uc758 \uc6b0\uc704\ub97c \uc810\ud558\uc138\uc694. \uc0b0\uc18d\uc744 \ud0d0\ud5d8\ud558\uace0 \ub3c4\uc2dc\uc758 \ube4c\ub529\uc744 \uc624\ub974\uba70 \ub85c\ud504 \uc5c6\uc774 \ud074\ub77c\uc774\ubc0d\ud558\ub294 \uc9dc\ub9bf\ud568\uc744 \ub290\ub07c\uace0, \uc0c8\ub85c\uc6b4 \uace0\uc9c0\uc5d0 \ub3c4\ub2ec\ud574 \uc228 \uba4e\uc744 \ub4ef\ud55c \ud48d\uad11\uc744 \uac10\uc0c1\ud558\uc138\uc694.", "short_description": "The Climb 2\ub294 \uc0c8\ub85c\uc6b4 \ub3c4\uc2dc \ubc30\uacbd, \ud765\ubbf8\ub85c\uc6b4 \uc2e0\uaddc \ub9f5, \uc2e0\uaddc \uc774\ubca4\ud2b8 \ub4f1\uc73c\ub85c \uc2a4\ub9b4\uc744 \uc120\ubb3c\ud569\ub2c8\ub2e4. \uc0b0 \uc815\uc0c1\uae4c\uc9c0 \ub4f1\ubc18\ud558\uace0, \ub4dc\ub113\uc740 \ub3d9\uad74\uc744 \ud0d0\ud5d8\ud558\uace0, \uace0\uce35 \uac74\ubb3c\uc744 \uc624\ub974\uace0, \uc9c0\ub984\uae38\uc744 \ubc1c\uacac\ud574 \uaf2d\ub300\uae30\uc5d0 \ub3c4\ub2ec\ud558\uc138\uc694. \uba40\ud2f0\ud50c\ub808\uc774 \ubaa8\ub4dc\uc5d0\uc11c \ub9ac\ub354\ubcf4\ub4dc\uc758 \uc0c1\uc704\uad8c\uc744 \ub193\uace0 \uce5c\uad6c\uc640 \uc6b0\uc704\ub97c \ub2e4\ud22c\uc138\uc694."}, {"images": {"nodes": []}, "id": "772618826896246", "locale": "fr_FR", "screenshots": [], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "The Climb 2", "keywords": ["Sports"], "long_description": "Avec The Climb 2, les sensations de l'escalade sont plus intenses que jamais. Explorez un nouvel environnement urbain et des maps in\u00e9dites offrant des vues \u00e0 couper le souffle. Ascensionnez des pics grandioses, aventurez-vous au c\u0153ur de grottes gigantesques, escaladez des gratte-ciel vertigineux et d\u00e9couvrez des raccourcis savamment dissimul\u00e9s qui vous m\u00e8neront tout droit au firmament ! Affrontez des amis et hissez-vous au top des classements en mode multijoueur asynchrone ! Du relief escarp\u00e9 des r\u00e9gions montagneuses aux paysages r\u00e9solument citadins, ressentez les pouss\u00e9es d'adr\u00e9naline que procure l'escalade sans corde et laissez-vous griser par des horizons extraordinaires lorsque vous atteindrez de nouveaux sommets.", "short_description": "Avec The Climb 2, les sensations de l'escalade sont plus intenses que jamais. Au programme : un nouvel environnement urbain, des maps in\u00e9dites, des \u00e9v\u00e9nements exclusifs et bien plus encore ! Ascensionnez des pics extraordinaires, aventurez-vous au c\u0153ur de grottes gigantesques, escaladez des gratte-ciel vertigineux et d\u00e9couvrez des raccourcis qui vous m\u00e8neront tout droit au sommet ! Affrontez des amis en multijoueur et hissez-vous au top des classements !"}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "Store_Hero_3000x900.png", "id": "724297951601109", "image_type": "APP_IMG_HERO", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75469622_724297958267775_4885988412130877578_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=mzKDjTlu2QQQ7kNvgEfnRoC&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBVgbHy0q_EqhQd0G4U4F9OxheMkh1T8rAtLpTK2m7vrA&oe=66D99F64"}, {"file_name": "Store_Icon_512x512.png", "id": "714703862741851", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75210896_714703866075184_526865366033963965_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=2ozImVtKAP0Q7kNvgFMcq